Entity Task

Action perform_task_creation
  EventInput
    space_id, title, start_date, due_date, autoclose_date   required
    description, reference_task_id                           optional
  BusinessRules
    - space_id must reference an Active Space owned by the actor
    - due_date must be >= start_date
    - autoclose_date must be >= due_date
    - If reference_task_id provided: referenced task must exist in the same space
  Steps
    - Create Task record with status = Pending
    - activity_id = null (manual creation)
  SideEffects
    - Trigger create_automatic_note with type = task_created
  ActionResult
    task_id   UUID

Action perform_task_update
  EventInput
    task_id                         required
    title, description, start_date,
    due_date, autoclose_date        optional
  BusinessRules
    - At least one field must be provided
    - If due_date provided: must be >= start_date (existing or new)
    - If autoclose_date provided: must be >= due_date (existing or new)
  Steps
    - Update provided fields on Task record
  SideEffects
    - None  (ChangeLog records all field changes — visible to user as history)
  ActionResult
    task_id         UUID
    updated_fields  string[]

Action perform_task_start
  EventInput
    task_id   required
  Steps
    - Update Task status to InProgress
  SideEffects
    - Trigger create_automatic_note with type = task_status_changed
  ActionResult
    task_id           UUID
    previous_status   TaskStatus
    new_status        InProgress

Action perform_task_complete
  EventInput
    task_id   required
  Steps
    - Update Task status to Completed
  SideEffects
    - Trigger create_automatic_note with type = task_status_changed
  ActionResult
    task_id           UUID
    previous_status   TaskStatus
    new_status        Completed

Action perform_task_skip
  EventInput
    task_id   required
  Steps
    - Update Task status to Skipped
  SideEffects
    - Trigger create_automatic_note with type = task_status_changed
  ActionResult
    task_id           UUID
    previous_status   TaskStatus
    new_status        Skipped

Action perform_task_reopen
  EventInput
    task_id   required
  Steps
    - Update Task status to Pending
  SideEffects
    - Trigger create_automatic_note with type = task_status_changed
  ActionResult
    task_id           UUID
    previous_status   TaskStatus
    new_status        Pending

Action perform_add_task_comment
  EventInput
    task_id   required
    content   required
  Steps
    - Create TaskComment record with status = Active
  SideEffects
    - Trigger create_automatic_note with type = task_comment_added
  ActionResult
    comment_id  UUID
    task_id     UUID

Action perform_update_task_comment
  EventInput
    task_id     required
    comment_id  required
    content     required
  BusinessRules
    - comment_id must belong to task_id
    - TaskComment status must be Active
  Steps
    - Update TaskComment content
  SideEffects
    - None  (ChangeLog records the change)
  ActionResult
    comment_id  UUID

Action perform_archive_task_comment
  EventInput
    task_id     required
    comment_id  required
  BusinessRules
    - comment_id must belong to task_id
    - TaskComment status must be Active
  Steps
    - Update TaskComment status to Archived
  SideEffects
    - None
  ActionResult
    comment_id  UUID

Action perform_task_autoclose
  EventInput
    task_id   required
  BusinessRules
    - autoclose_date must be <= today
  Steps
    - Update Task status to AutoClosed
  SideEffects
    - Trigger create_automatic_note with type = task_autoclosed
  ActionResult
    task_id   UUID

Action perform_task_archive
  EventInput
    task_id   required
  BusinessRules
    - Task must have been in Completed | Skipped | AutoClosed for >= 14 days
      (measured from the timestamp of the last status change in ChangeLog)
  Steps
    - Update Task status to Archived
  SideEffects
    - None  (archive is silent — no automatic note)
  ActionResult
    task_id   UUID

Action reject_request
  Steps
    - No state change
  Outcome
    NoAction    REQUEST_REJECTED

Action skip_autoclose
  Steps
    - No state change. Task is already in a terminal or Archived state.
  Outcome
    NoAction    AUTOCLOSE_SKIPPED

Action skip_archive
  Steps
    - No state change. Task is not in an archivable state.
  Outcome
    NoAction    ARCHIVE_SKIPPED
